{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.1","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:1","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.013.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Amatsia, roi de Juda<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-22: cf. (2 Ch 25; 26:1-2.) Ps 75:5-8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La seconde ann\u00e9e de Joas, fils de Joachaz, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, Amatsia, fils de Joas, roi de Juda, r\u00e9gna.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.2","name":"2 Rois 14:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.13.25","name":"2 Rois 13:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.13.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.2","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:2","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il avait vingt-cinq ans lorsqu\u2019il devint roi, et il r\u00e9gna vingt-neuf ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Joaddan, de J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.3","name":"2 Rois 14:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.1","name":"2 Rois 14:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.3","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:3","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est droit aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, non pas toutefois comme David, son p\u00e8re; il agit enti\u00e8rement comme avait agi Joas, son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.4","name":"2 Rois 14:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.2","name":"2 Rois 14:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.4","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:4","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Seulement, les hauts lieux ne disparurent point; le peuple offrait encore des sacrifices et des parfums sur les hauts lieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.5","name":"2 Rois 14:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.3","name":"2 Rois 14:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.5","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:5","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Lorsque la royaut\u00e9 fut affermie entre ses mains, il frappa ses serviteurs qui avaient tu\u00e9 le roi, son p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.6","name":"2 Rois 14:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.4","name":"2 Rois 14:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.6","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:6","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Mais il ne fit pas mourir les fils des meurtriers, selon ce qui est \u00e9crit dans le livre de la loi de Mo\u00efse, o\u00f9 l\u2019\u00c9ternel donne ce commandement: On ne fera point mourir les p\u00e8res pour les enfants, et l\u2019on ne fera point mourir les enfants pour les p\u00e8res; mais on fera mourir chacun pour son p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.7","name":"2 Rois 14:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.5","name":"2 Rois 14:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.7","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:7","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Il battit dix mille \u00c9domites dans la vall\u00e9e du sel; et durant la guerre, il prit S\u00e9la, et l\u2019appela Joktheel, nom qu\u2019elle a conserv\u00e9 jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.8","name":"2 Rois 14:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.6","name":"2 Rois 14:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.8","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:8","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Alors Amatsia envoya des messagers \u00e0 Joas, fils de Joachaz, fils de J\u00e9hu, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, pour lui dire: Viens, voyons-nous en face!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.9","name":"2 Rois 14:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.7","name":"2 Rois 14:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.9","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:9","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Et Joas, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, fit dire \u00e0 Amatsia, roi de Juda: L\u2019\u00e9pine du Liban envoya dire au c\u00e8dre du Liban: Donne ta fille pour femme \u00e0 mon fils! Et les b\u00eates sauvages qui sont au Liban pass\u00e8rent et foul\u00e8rent l\u2019\u00e9pine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.10","name":"2 Rois 14:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.8","name":"2 Rois 14:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.10","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:10","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Tu as battu les \u00c9domites, et ton c\u0153ur s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve. Jouis de ta gloire, et reste chez toi. Pourquoi t\u2019engager dans une malheureuse entreprise, qui am\u00e8nerait ta ruine et celle de Juda?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.11","name":"2 Rois 14:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.9","name":"2 Rois 14:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.11","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:11","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Mais Amatsia ne l\u2019\u00e9couta pas. Et Joas, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, monta; et ils se virent en face, lui et Amatsia, roi de Juda, \u00e0 Beth-Sch\u00e9mesch, qui est \u00e0 Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.12","name":"2 Rois 14:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.10","name":"2 Rois 14:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.12","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:12","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Juda fut battu par Isra\u00ebl, et chacun s\u2019enfuit dans sa tente.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.13","name":"2 Rois 14:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.11","name":"2 Rois 14:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.13","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:13","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Joas, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, prit \u00e0 Beth-Sch\u00e9mesch Amatsia, roi de Juda, fils de Joas, fils d\u2019Achazia. Il vint \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, et fit une br\u00e8che de quatre cents coud\u00e9es dans la muraille de J\u00e9rusalem, depuis la porte d\u2019\u00c9phra\u00efm jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la porte de l\u2019angle.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.14","name":"2 Rois 14:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.12","name":"2 Rois 14:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.14","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:14","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Il prit tout l\u2019or et l\u2019argent et tous les vases qui se trouvaient dans la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel et dans les tr\u00e9sors de la maison du roi; il prit aussi des otages, et il retourna \u00e0 Samarie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.15","name":"2 Rois 14:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.13","name":"2 Rois 14:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.15","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:15","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Joas, ce qu\u2019il a fait, ses exploits, et la guerre qu\u2019il eut avec Amatsia, roi de Juda, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.16","name":"2 Rois 14:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.14","name":"2 Rois 14:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.16","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:16","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Joas se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, et il fut enterr\u00e9 \u00e0 Samarie avec les rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. Et J\u00e9roboam, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.17","name":"2 Rois 14:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.15","name":"2 Rois 14:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.17","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:17","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Amatsia, fils de Joas, roi de Juda, v\u00e9cut quinze ans apr\u00e8s la mort de Joas, fils de Joachaz, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.18","name":"2 Rois 14:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.16","name":"2 Rois 14:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.18","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:18","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Le reste des actions d\u2019Amatsia, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois de Juda?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.19","name":"2 Rois 14:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.17","name":"2 Rois 14:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.19","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:19","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>On forma contre lui une conspiration \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, et il s\u2019enfuit \u00e0 Lakis; mais on le poursuivit \u00e0 Lakis, o\u00f9 on le fit mourir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.20","name":"2 Rois 14:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.18","name":"2 Rois 14:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.20","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:20","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>On le transporta sur des chevaux, et il fut enterr\u00e9 \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem avec ses p\u00e8res, dans la ville de David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.21","name":"2 Rois 14:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.19","name":"2 Rois 14:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.21","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:21","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et tout le peuple de Juda prit Azaria, \u00e2g\u00e9 de seize ans, et l\u2019\u00e9tablit roi \u00e0 la place de son p\u00e8re Amatsia.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.22","name":"2 Rois 14:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.20","name":"2 Rois 14:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.22","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:22","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Azaria reb\u00e2tit \u00c9lath et la fit rentrer sous la puissance de Juda, apr\u00e8s que le roi fut couch\u00e9 avec ses p\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.23","name":"2 Rois 14:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.21","name":"2 Rois 14:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.23","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:23","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.024,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">J\u00e9roboam II, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 23-29: cf. Am 1-7. Jon 1-4. Os 1-3.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>La quinzi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e d\u2019Amatsia, fils de Joas, roi de Juda, J\u00e9roboam, fils de Joas, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 Samarie. Il r\u00e9gna quarante et un ans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.24","name":"2 Rois 14:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.22","name":"2 Rois 14:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.24","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:24","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel; il ne se d\u00e9tourna d\u2019aucun des p\u00e9ch\u00e9s de J\u00e9roboam, fils de Nebath, qui avait fait p\u00e9cher Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.25","name":"2 Rois 14:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.23","name":"2 Rois 14:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.25","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:25","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Il r\u00e9tablit les limites d\u2019Isra\u00ebl depuis l\u2019entr\u00e9e de Hamath jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la mer de la plaine, selon la parole que l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, avait prononc\u00e9e par son serviteur Jonas, le proph\u00e8te, fils d\u2019Amittha\u00ef, de Gath-H\u00e9pher.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.26","name":"2 Rois 14:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.24","name":"2 Rois 14:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.26","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:26","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Car l\u2019\u00c9ternel vit l\u2019affliction d\u2019Isra\u00ebl \u00e0 son comble et l\u2019extr\u00e9mit\u00e9 \u00e0 laquelle se trouvaient r\u00e9duits esclaves et hommes libres, sans qu\u2019il y e\u00fbt personne pour venir au secours d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.27","name":"2 Rois 14:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.25","name":"2 Rois 14:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.27","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:27","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Or l\u2019\u00c9ternel n\u2019avait point r\u00e9solu d\u2019effacer le nom d\u2019Isra\u00ebl de dessous les cieux, et il les d\u00e9livra par J\u00e9roboam, fils de Joas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.28","name":"2 Rois 14:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.26","name":"2 Rois 14:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.28","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:28","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Le reste des actions de J\u00e9roboam, tout ce qu\u2019il a fait, ses exploits \u00e0 la guerre, et comment il fit rentrer sous la puissance d\u2019Isra\u00ebl Damas et Hamath qui avaient appartenu \u00e0 Juda, cela n\u2019est-il pas \u00e9crit dans le livre des Chroniques des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.29","name":"2 Rois 14:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.27","name":"2 Rois 14:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.29","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 14:29","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.014.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.015.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.14.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>J\u00e9roboam se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, avec les rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. Et Zacharie, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14","name":"2 Rois 14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.1","name":"2 Rois 15:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.15.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.28","name":"2 Rois 14:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.14.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb463cb09.69600778');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb463cb09.69600778\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb463cb09.69600778","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb463cb09.69600778'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb463cb09.69600778\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}